comments: Sengun (HOU) firms up on his right leg and marginal contact occurs with Maledon (CHA) as he goes over the pick.
McGowens (CHA) moves alongside Green's (HOU) path and absorbs the marginal contact during the driving shot attempt.
Williams (CHA) is drawn into the air and he comes down into Sengun (HOU), initiating contact that affects the layup attempt at the basket.
Williams' (CHA) arm lightly brushes Smith Jr. (HOU) as he navigates around the screen. The contact on the play is marginal.
Williams (CHA) extends his right arm outwards during the screen, but the contact with Porter Jr. (HOU) is marginal.
Maledon (CHA) aligns along Porter Jr.'s (HOU) path at the start of his dribble and marginal contact occurs.
Porter Jr.'s (HOU) off-arm comes out slightly and brushes Maledon (CHA) as Porter Jr. absorbs the marginal contact at the start of his dribble.
Maledon's (CHA) forearm brushes Porter Jr.'s (HOU) front as the pick is set and the contact is marginal.
McGowens (CHA) moves alongside Green's (HOU) path and absorbs the marginal contact during the drive.
McGowens (CHA) legally contests Green's (HOU) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Sengun (HOU) and Williams (CHA) come together at the same spot on the floor and the contact during the rebounding opportunity is marginal.
McGowens (CHA) brings his left arm toward the ball and marginal arm contact occurs with Green (HOU), which he is able to play on through.
Williams (CHA) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Green's (HOU) layup attempt.
Smith Jr. (HOU) legally contests Thor's (CHA) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Green (HOU) firms up in Maledon's (CHA) path and marginal contact occurs as they come together during the pick.
Williams (CHA) grasps and then promptly releases the back of Sengun's (HOU) jersey off-ball.
Thor (CHA) rests his left hand on Sengun's (HOU) side as he receives the pass and the contact is marginal.
Green (HOU) reaches in for the ball and lower body contact occurs with Mykhailiuk (CHA) that affects his SQBR.
Porter Jr. (HOU) establishes himself in McGowens' (CHA) path and does not deliver illegal contact when setting the pick.
Maledon (CHA) slides his forearm off of Green's (HOU) side after his gather and the contact during the driving shot attempt is marginal.
Eason (HOU) and McGowens (CHA) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs during the inbound.
Smith Jr.'s (HOU) is in a legal vertical position when contact occurs with Mykhailiuk (CHA), who leans in to create the marginal contact.
Eason (HOU) briefly holds his arms out behind him and marginal contact occurs with Williams (CHA) as the two players engage and disengage.
Mykhailiuk (CHA) commits a take foul on Martin Jr. (HOU). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of the fourth quarter and overtime.
Maledon (CHA) is inside the three-point arc prior to Martin Jr.'s (HOU) release of the free throw attempt.
Williams (CHA) firms up on his right leg and marginal lower body contact occurs with Smith Jr. (HOU) as he navigates over the pick.
Maledon (CHA) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes two steps before releasing his pass.
Smith Jr. (HOU) legally contests Mykhailiuk's (CHA) perimeter jump shot attempt.
Green (HOU) legally contests Mykhailiuk's (CHA) perimeter jump shot attempt.
